# NOTE: repo skills/ are shipped defaults (tracked); the runtime skill
# library lives in ~/.maro/workspace/skills/ (outside the repo). An old
# blanket `skills/` ignore here silently kept the 1.0 ship-set skills and
# src/maro_assets/skills/ symlinks out of e0811c7 — don't reintroduce it.

